The '''Klagg tribe''', also known as the '''Klagg clan''', was a clan of [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]] native to [[Pzob/Legends|Pzob]]. In [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]] they were captured along with [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], his companions, their rival clan, the [[Gakfedd tribe|Gakfedds]] and indoctrinated onboard the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] battlemoon, ''[[Eye of Palpatine]]''. Their indoctrination was almost successful; the Klaggs learned to speak [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] and were turned into relatively good [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtroopers]]. They constantly considered the Gakfedd's to be [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]], and fought each other consistently. When they were evacuated from the battlemoon, they refused reorientation and negotiated with [[Drost Elegin]] to be taken on as bodyguards.

